 place\", \"from\": 628, \"to\": 639}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Championships\", \"from\": 643, \"to\": 666}, {\"ngram\": \"Sharjah\", \"from\": 670, \"to\": 677}, {\"ngram\": \"the 13th spot\", \"from\": 700, \"to\": 713}, {\"ngram\": \"global rankings\", \"from\": 717, \"to\": 732}, {\"ngram\": \"inThe Mirror\", \"from\": 746, \"to\": 758}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alongside Brown, and veteran skater Andy MacDonald, aged 51, the trio are set to make their mark on the podium when they take to their boards this week.\", \"from\": 761, \"to\": 913, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 797, \"end\": 811, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Macdonald_(skateboarder)\", \"score\": 0.7012169389860421, \"rank\": 0.42608695652174866, \"text\": \"Andy MacDonald\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Macdonald_(skateboarder)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Macdonald_(skateboarder)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Brown\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 776}, {\"ngram\": \"the trio\", \"from\": 822, \"to\": 830}, {\"ngram\": \"their mark\", \"from\": 847, \"to\": 857}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 861, \"to\": 871}, {\"ngram\": \"their boards\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 902}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The three hopefuls navigated a two-part Olympic Qualifying Series (OQS) to secure their spots in Paris.\", \"from\": 914, \"to\": 1017, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1011, \"end\": 1016, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.427504182373182e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The three hopefuls\", \"from\": 914, \"to\": 932}, {\"ngram\": \"a two-part Olympic Qualifying Series\", \"from\": 943, \"to\": 979}, {\"ngram\": \"OQS\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 984}, {\"ngram\": \"their spots\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1007}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Impressively, Tambling managed to amass enough points to qualify as one of the top 22 skaters even without competing in the final.\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1149, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tambling\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1041}, {\"ngram\": \"enough points\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1072}, {\"ngram\": \"the top 22 skaters\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1112}, {\"ngram\": \"the final\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1148}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From a tender age of seven, Tambling took to the skateboard like a natural after her father Martyn, himself a professional BMX rider, constructed a skate park for her.By the age of 11, she was already clinching titles in competitions, and although she had an affinity for her father's sport, skateboarding ultimately captured her heart.\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1486, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1273, \"end\": 1282, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"score\": 0.9999999999854481, \"rank\": 1.4705834224630417e-11, \"text\": \"BMX rider\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a tender age\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1167}, {\"ngram\": \"Tambling\", \"from\": 1178, \"to\": 1186}, {\"ngram\": \"the skateboard\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1209}, {\"ngram\": \"her father\", \"from\": 1231, \"to\": 1241}, {\"ngram\": \"Martyn\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1248}, {\"ngram\": \"a skate park\", \"from\": 1296, \"to\": 1308}, {\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 1320, \"to\": 1327}, {\"ngram\": \"titles\", \"from\": 1361, \"to\": 1367}, {\"ngram\": \"competitions\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1383}, {\"ngram\": \"an affinity\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1417}, {\"ngram\": \"her father's sport\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1440}, {\"ngram\": \"her heart\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1485}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have always grown up around the BMX and skateboarding scene,\\\" Tambling shared withTeam GB's website.\", \"from\": 1488, \"to\": 1591, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1523, \"end\": 1526, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"score\": 0.9999999998840394, \"rank\": 9.271169574753012e-11, \"text\": \"BMX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\"}, {\"begin\": 1578, \"end\": 1580, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9401812140066397, \"rank\": 0.06362473795216458, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Maybe I would have done BMXing but I was like, nah, skating's the one.\\\"\", \"from\": 1592, \"to\": 1664, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"BMXing\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1623}, {\"ngram\": \"skating\", \"from\": 1645, \"to\": 1652}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Witnessing her team-mate Brown secure an Olympic bronze in 2021 was a pivotal moment for Tambling.\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1766, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her team-mate Brown\", \"from\": 1679, \"to\": 1698}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic bronze\", \"from\": 1706, \"to\": 1723}, {\"ngram\": \"a pivotal moment\", \"from\": 1736, \"to\": 1752}, {\"ngram\": \"Tambling\", \"from\": 1757, \"to\": 1765}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bolstered by Brown's success and her own burgeoning track record, she began to trust in her own convictions that has now catapulted her to the pinnacle of sport, the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1767, \"to\": 1947, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Brown's success\", \"from\": 1780, \"to\": 1795}, {\"ngram\": \"her own burgeoning track record\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1831}, {\"ngram\": \"her own convictions\", \"from\": 1855, \"to\": 1874}, {\"ngram\": \"the pinnacle\", \"from\": 1906, \"to\": 1918}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1922, \"to\": 1927}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1929, \"to\": 1946}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reflecting on her performance at the World Championships in Sharjah where she placed sixth, Tambling expressed her newfound confidence: \\\"Last year in Sharjah, when I came sixth at the World Champs, I thought I am actually up there, I am good enough, I am with all the top (skateboarders),\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1949, \"to\": 2248, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2099, \"end\": 2106, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sharjah\", \"score\": 0.920659111234729, \"rank\": 0.08464401779172766, \"text\": \"Sharjah\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sharjah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sharjah\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her performance\", \"from\": 1963, \"to\": 1978}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Championships\", \"from\": 1982, \"to\": 2005}, {\"ngram\": \"Sharjah\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2016}, {\"ngram\": \"Tambling\", \"from\": 2041, \"to\": 2049}, {\"ngram\": \"her newfound confidence\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2083}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Champs\", \"from\": 2129, \"to\": 2145}, {\"ngram\": \"all the top (skateboarders\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2235}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is the start and if I keep going, I could definitely make it.\", \"from\": 2249, \"to\": 2316, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 2258, \"to\": 2267}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Because I have made it into the top 20, I am in a really good spot.\\\"\", \"from\": 2317, \"to\": 2385, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a really good spot\", \"from\": 2365, \"to\": 2383}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The meteoric ascent of the talented young star has seen her become a sensation not only on the half-pipe but also on the fashion runway, collaborating with iconic brands such as Ben Sherman and Adidas.\", \"from\": 2387, \"to\": 2588, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2565, \"end\": 2576, \"title\":